sentences: Jo Eun-sim (Korean: 조은심; born December 26, 1986), better known by her stage name, Song Ga-in (Korean: 송가인), is a South Korean female trot singer.
She is the winner of the 2019 reality television show Miss Trot.
Song was born Jo Eun-shim on December 26, 1986 in Jindo County, South Jeolla Province, South Korea.
